# Portrait Gemini ingest

## Mandatory reads (before any portrait art or ingest work)

1. [`docs/vision/references/PORTRAIT_REFERENCE_BOARD.md`](../../docs/vision/references/PORTRAIT_REFERENCE_BOARD.md)
2. [`docs/vision/GEMINI_ART_BRIEF.md`](../../docs/vision/GEMINI_ART_BRIEF.md)
3. [`docs/vision/COMPOSER_PLAYBOOK.md`](../../docs/vision/COMPOSER_PLAYBOOK.md)
4. [`docs/vision/ASSET_INGESTION.md`](../../docs/vision/ASSET_INGESTION.md)

## Hard rules

- **NEVER** draw, redraw, or edit portrait SVG art in agent sessions
- **NEVER** illustrate bust PNGs — owner creates art in Google Gemini Pro Art mode
- **Ingest only** from `static/portrait/approved/` — owner-approved PNGs with `ASSET_LICENSES.md` row ☑
- **One bust per ingest sprint** — sprint id `3.5m-gemini-ingest`
- Mark ROADMAP sprint **Done** only after owner **holo approved ☑** on `/player/dashboard` — automated tests alone are insufficient (see 3.5l-gate lesson)

## Composer pipeline (agents)

```bash
firebase use sports-skill-tracker-dev
npm run generate:portraits
npm test -- src/lib/gamification/__tests__/playerLoadoutSprint35*.test.ts
npm run check
npm run build
firebase deploy --only hosting
```

## Superseded

- **3.5m-art** — agent modular SVG bust redraw; human VA failed. Shipping path = Gemini precomposed busts + ingest.

